differs from the classic preloaded-FIFO replay, so the detected single/double/triple
click sequence is time-shifted from expected (values differ; pin set matches). Needs
the streamer advance to be paced one-line-per-thread-cycle (or the sampler start
aligned) for timing-sensitive stateful comps. (Stateless streaming comps like abs.0
convert cleanly.)
